# SEO

## Single source of truth

- `src/lib/site.ts` — `siteConfig`, `openGraphLocales`
- Copy: `dictionary/{locale}/Metadata` (`title`, `description`, `keywords`)

## Canonical and hreflang URLs

Use `getLocaleUrl` / `getAlternateLanguages` from `@/lib/site` — never duplicate hreflang maps in layout and sitemap.

```ts
const canonical = await getLocaleUrl(locale, "/your-path");
const languages = await getAlternateLanguages("/your-path");
```

| Locale | Path |
|--------|------|
| `en` | `/` |
| others | `/{locale}` |

## `generateMetadata`

- Set `metadataBase: new URL(siteConfig.url)`.
- `alternates.canonical` + `alternates.languages` for all `routing.locales`.
- OG image: `/og-image.png` (1200×630 in `public/`).

## Sitemap (`src/app/sitemap.ts`)

- One entry per logical page with `alternates.languages` — not duplicate rows per locale.
- New pages: add entry with `getPathname({ locale, href: "/your-path" })` for each locale.

## New page SEO checklist

1. Meta keys in all dictionary files
2. Page-level `generateMetadata` with canonical
3. Sitemap entry with hreflang alternates
4. Optional JSON-LD in Server Component only
